Read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root — it is the single source of truth for this project.

Non-negotiables:
- Remote icon switching = SELECT among build-time-bundled alternates via Firebase Remote
  Config. NEVER imply you can push a new icon image over the air; a new theme needs an app
  update.
- Icon model: per-product solid background color + white symbol (flagship `buky` = forest
  bg + mint symbol). No badges/strips/corner decorations — those are rejected.
- 3-layer master: full-bleed `bg` (no baked corners/effects), transparent `fg` symbol at
  safeZone 0.56 centered on the real ink bbox, `mono` silhouette for themed/tinted.
- `brand.config.json` is the source of truth; ESM `.mjs` scripts; deps light; mark
  paid/hosting/Xcode steps as `// STUB:`.
